1 (6) Restricted funds means (a) property tax, excluding any amounts
2 refunded to taxpayers, (b) payments in lieu of property taxes, (c) local
3 option sales taxes, (d) motor vehicle taxes, (e) state aid, (f) transfers
4 of surpluses from any user fee, permit fee, or regulatory fee if the fee
